---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Quest Labs — About">

<div class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-eyebrow">Quest Labs · The Creator</div>
  <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
  <p class="about-sub">The practitioner-researcher behind the methodology.</p>
</div>

<div class="about-grid">
  <div class="about-image-block">
    <img src="/makeda.JPG" alt="Makēda Gershenson" class="about-photo" />
  </div>

  <div class="about-text-block">
    <div class="about-section-label">Makēda</div>
    <h2 class="about-name">Quest Prime · Practitioner-Researcher</h2>
    <p>Since 2008, Makēda Gershenson has been building playgrounds for the future. As founder of Quest Labs | Mosaics in the Making, she facilitates sandbox sessions and research collaborations that function less like classrooms and more like portals — places where play becomes possibility and constraints are composted.</p>
    <p>Her work dances between the collision point of education, workforce evolution, and radical foresight, weaving decolonial scholarship and embodied practice into experiences that move people from what they've inherited to what they're brave enough to create.</p>
    <p>She doesn't do either/or: her approach holds the tension between rigor and relevance, inquiry and artistry, and analysis with care.</p>
    <p>Whether facilitating sandbox sessions that crack open new capacities, conducting organizational research that remaps who holds power over tomorrow, or exploring how a single metaphor can unlock what once seemed impossible, Makēda creates the conditions for you to see the stories you've been living inside… and then craft a different future together.</p>
    <p>A practice of not imagining alone, but in constellations.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 3rem;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .about-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .about-sub {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 5rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-image-block {
    padding-right: 3rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-text-block {
    padding-left: 3rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
  }

  .about-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .about-text-block p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-image-block {
      padding-right: 0;
    }

    .about-text-block {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
